The '''Imperial Intelligence Headquarters''' was located in the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was used as a base of operations for [[Armand Isard/Legends|Armand Isard's]] [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]]. One of the headquarters building's main hallways, lined with tall pillars, had the emblem of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] emblazoned on the tiled floor.

